column1: Live births by area, city/district councils (Maori and total population) (Annual-Dec)
Births exclude late registrations under section 16 of the Births, Deaths, Marriages, and Relationships Registration Act 1995.
Births are based on births registered in New Zealand to mothers resident in New Zealand by date of registration.

Boundaries: Data before 2006 is based on boundaries for the year of registration. Data for 2006-10 is on 2006 boundaries, 2011-12 on 2011 boundaries, 2013-17 on 2013 boundaries. From 2018, data is based on 2018 boundaries.
Figures for the Auckland Council for March, June, and September 2011 year are estimated using a combination of 2006 and 2011 boundaries.
Data has been randomly rounded to protect confidentiality. Individual figures may not add up to totals, and values for the same data may vary in different tables.
